1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:19,820
The Legend of Awakening

3
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:22,579
Episode 34

4
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:24,720
Qin Sang.

5
00:02:24,810 --> 00:02:25,640
Qin Sang.

6
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,400
You are not qualified to mention her name.

7
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,840
If she doesn’t care about me,

8
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:31,520
she won’t curse me while

9
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:33,240
asking you to protect me.

10
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:37,160
All she thinks is you.

11
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,000
But what did you do for her?

12
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,400
If it weren’t for you,

13
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:42,240
General Qin wouldn’t die.

14
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,600
Had it not been for you,

15
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,880
Princess wouldn’t put herself in danger.

16
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:47,320
I should have you killed in Kaifeng

17
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:49,040
if I had known it.

18
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,880
You deserve dying for

19
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,360
what you have done.

20
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,080
Why don’t you kill me?

21
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:15,320
We only kill enemies.

22
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,329
We don’t kill innocent people.

23
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,730
I will not let your blood

24
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,640
ruin our reputation.

25
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,930
You are really a soldier following Qin Qi.

26
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,160
Tell me.

27
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:32,810
What did Princess ask you to do?

28
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,000
She asked me

29
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,640
to escort you to Big Dipper at night

30
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,440
and stop you from coming back.

31
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:41,640
She is putting fine timber to petty use.

32
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,640
You know you are petty.

33
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,680
I should stay with Princess

34
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,240
to fight against Shanhai Gang.

35
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:49,960
But now.

36
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,170
What did you say?

37
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:53,579
Qin Sang is framing Shanhai Gang?

38
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,079
Yes.

39
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,540
She would not have been a princess

40
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,760
but for the elimination of the gang.

41
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,700
She wouldn’t marry Yan Xifan.

42
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,400
Wen Rui,

43
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,170
you are worried about Qin Sang.

44
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:07,090
What about letting me go

45
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:09,180
and we are going to find her together?

46
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:10,600
No.

47
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,680
I must obey the military order.

48
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:14,580
Otherwise,

49
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,600
I can’t fulfill my responsibility later.

50
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,950
You are silly.

51
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,200
She is pushing me away.

52
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:21,260
It proves that she is in great danger.

53
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,080
If we don’t come for help,

54
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,040
you wouldn’t see her again

55
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,960
in case she got killed.

56
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,200
Wen Rui,

57
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,080
I beg you.

58
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,640
How can we let

59
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,600
a girl to fight

60
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,930
against the enemy while

61
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,280
staying back ourselves?

62
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,400
Hurry up.

63
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:04,960
Arrows.

64
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,320
Lu Ping.

65
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:23,440
Stop.

66
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,159
Princess.

67
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,360
What?

68
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,320
Yan Qiuci left the manor at dusk.

69
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,320
He just came back.

70
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,800
We saw Ling Ziyan in the manor.

71
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,320
She was packing up.

72
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,730
She seemed to leave.

73
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,480
OK.

74
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,800
Ziyan was always in Wuji Manor.

75
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,680
I have to bet on

76
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,200
his love for me.

77
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,640
Ziyan.

78
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,280
Miss.

79
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,280
I will wait for you

80
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,690
at midnight outside the manor.

81
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,760
I will be with you

82
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,880
wherever you go.

83
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:05,840
Ziyan,

84
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,360
can you stay?

85
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,320
Why?

86
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,920
Why don’t you let me go?

87
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,240
Lu Ping and Xifan.

88
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:18,560
Why do you always take

89
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:20,160
my only precious easily?

90
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:23,000
Why do you always stand in front of me?

91
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,600
If it is for Xifan,

92
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:28,160
you can’t go either.

93
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:30,960
I didn’t know that

94
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,640
you loved each other.

95
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,720
I didn’t imagine that I would meet you here.

96
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,400
I have to obey the marriage

97
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,730
offered by his majesty.

98
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:42,040
But I aim to kill Liu Song

99
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,780
and destroy the seal in Thousand Pine Ruler.

100
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,480
So what?

101
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,040
Ziyan,

102
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:52,560
we didn’t treat you well.

103
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:55,409
But I hope you can think of the country.

104
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,920
Please hold it back.

105
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,280
If we succeed,

106
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:04,400
I will marry you to Xifan.

107
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,540
What about your

108
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,680
own reputation?

109
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,410
It is Xining Princess who marries.

110
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:14,180
No one knows if she is Qin Sang.

111
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:16,160
You can be her.

112
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,370
You are really upright.

113
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,920
I can hardly match you.

114
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:22,920
Ziyan.

115
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,240
Princess is also here.

116
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,030
Go.

117
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:36,669
He hopes to answer you.

118
00:08:55,980 --> 00:08:58,380
[Wuji Manor]

119
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,250
Younger master.

120
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:25,890
Before Lu Ping left,

121
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,120
he asked me to be more brave

122
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,960
and follow my heart.

123
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:33,520
But I have something to do.

124
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,680
I have to help my father in Wuji Manor.

125
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:39,240
I have to cooperate with others against Shanhai Gang.

126
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:41,000
Lu Ping is an enemy of the gang.

127
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,770
He needs company

128
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,600
in the battle.

129
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,360
So you want to go

130
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,930
but you have to stay.

131
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,730
I promise you that after the

132
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:53,760
war against the gang,

133
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,200
I will marry you.

134
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,560
You haven’t asked me.

135
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:03,080
You are so impulsive.

136
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,520
I…

137
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:07,240
Ziyan,

138
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,600
I was too impulsive.

139
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:15,880
If you stay,

140
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,240
I will stay.

141
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,960
I know your ambition

142
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,160
and your goal.

143
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:25,360
I know that Miss would make it hard for you.

144
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:28,320
I can’t escape.

145
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:31,400
I will fight together with you

146
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,960
with all my strength.

147
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:35,050
I will be with you with dignity.

148
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:37,920
That is the meaning of my life.

149
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:41,240
And other…

150
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:47,440
I will take care of the other things.

151
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,600
Ziyan,

152
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:55,720
thank you.

153
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,600
Lu Ping,

154
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,120
I didn’t let you down.

155
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:52,840
Princess.

156
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,360
What’s up?

157
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:57,480
We were attacked by people from Shanhai Gang.

158
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:58,720
Lu Ping…

159
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:00,080
What happened to him?

160
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,240
Where is he?

161
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,200
He is missing.

162
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:05,440
We have searched nearby

163
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:07,120
but we failed to find him.

164
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,480
It is my fault.

165
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,120
Lu Ping.

166
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,040
Lu Ping.

167
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,640
Lu Ping.

168
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,840
Where are you?

169
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:35,760
Lu Ping.

170
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,600
Lu Ping.

171
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:45,880
Lu Ping.

172
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,080
Lu Ping.

173
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:54,920
Lu Ping.

174
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,520
It is my fault.

175
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,840
Please punish me.

176
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:05,760
Search.

177
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:08,090
Let all the soldiers to search for him.

178
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:10,200
Princess.

179
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:13,240
We are here for the gang.

180
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:15,600
Now that they have appeared,

181
00:13:15,920 --> 00:13:16,960
we should discuss with

182
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,840
Master Yan as soon as possible.

183
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,960
Then will I just let Lu Ping die?

184
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,840
I am a person.

185
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,920
I can’t be selfless now.

186
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:44,000
Leave a team of soldiers for searching.

187
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,920
Others go back to the manor.

188
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,040
Yes.

189
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:15,240
Do you know you would be beheaded?

190
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,720
Am I afraid of dying now?

191
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:37,440
It is just the glory of Qin Family.

192
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,720
I can help you, too.

193
00:14:44,520 --> 00:14:45,000
Lu Ping.

194
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:48,320
Are you alive or dead?

195
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,160
Where are you?

196
00:15:14,780 --> 00:15:18,980
[Wuji Manor]

197
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:25,040
You stayed up all night.

198
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:26,280
Have a rest.

199
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:29,490
Miss is searching for Lu Ping by all means.

200
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,440
Longjie Army isn’t familiar with the place.

201
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,840
I can serve as a guide.

202
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:35,080
I am responsible for it, too.

203
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:37,120
If I went together,

204
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,240
he would not be missing.

205
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,680
I just don’t understand.

206
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:44,120
How did Shanhai Gang sneaked into

207
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:46,640
and despite of the defense of the manor?

208
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:48,720
They are now trying to

209
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:50,240
break the Thousand Pine Ruler.

210
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:52,200
Why did they capture Lu Ping?

211
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,800
It is really strange.

212
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:56,840
Ziyan.

213
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,240
Please check the forest nearby.

214
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,480
I will search the lake where he disappeared.

215
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:03,010
Maybe I will find some clue.

216
00:16:25,020 --> 00:16:29,260
[Wuji]

217
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:27,720
Princess.

218
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:29,340
Master Yan.

219
00:16:29,880 --> 00:16:31,210
It has been a night since

220
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:34,080
Longjie Army was attacked and Lu Ping disappeared.

221
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,610
Shouldn’t we do something?

222
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,100
I have checked.

223
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:40,000
It is a blessing day after seven days.

224
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:42,520
We will hold the wedding on that day.

225
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:43,480
Master Yan.

226
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,560
I am not talking about the wedding

227
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:46,600
but Shanhai Gang.

228
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:52,000
The marriage is offered by his majesty.

229
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:55,000
We have sent the invitations.

230
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:56,960
How can it be canceled?

231
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:07,800
Are you checkmating me now?

232
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,520
I dare not.

233
00:17:14,069 --> 00:17:15,470
The wedding is a fake one.

234
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:18,280
Please give me Lyu Chenfeng soon.

235
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:19,520
His majesty ordered that…

236
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:20,400
Princess,

237
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,349
it is Wuji Manor here,

238
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,400
not Kaifeng.

239
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:26,520
I know how to do it better than you.

240
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:28,240
A Ze,

241
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:31,020
escort the Princess back.

242
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,060
Get prepared for the wedding.

243
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:33,760
Yes.

244
00:17:35,380 --> 00:17:36,070
Princess.

245
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:36,900
Please.

246
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,160
The manor is strange.

247
00:17:58,640 --> 00:17:59,970
We’d better be careful.

248
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:03,680
Have you made an agreement with Master Yan?

249
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:06,480
They have defended the manor well.

250
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,380
We can’t send message out.

251
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:10,320
We can neither organize our men.

252
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:12,930
Don’t you think that we have been imprisoned?

253
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:14,880
You mean…

254
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:17,120
Yan Qiuci delayed the wedding

255
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:19,720
as well we delayed the attack

256
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:20,980
towards Shanhai Gang.

257
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:23,560
He didn’t let me meet Lyu Chenfeng.

258
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:26,800
Why did he do that?

259
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:29,600
Princess.

260
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:31,560
I found a thing by the lake

261
00:18:31,760 --> 00:18:33,020
which I have to report.

262
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,060
Please have a look.

263
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,240
An eagle feather of iron?

264
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:43,720
Yes.

265
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,620
I learned from the general

266
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:47,800
and put my Force of Color into my arrows.

267
00:18:47,800 --> 00:18:49,330
They can be extremely fast.

268
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:51,640
This is the arrow I shot

269
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,800
when I was attacked that day.

270
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:55,880
The one who broke it must be

271
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:58,280
learning Force of Color.

272
00:18:58,760 --> 00:19:00,520
He may be more powerful than you.

273
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:03,000
I have fought with Shanhai Gang several times.

274
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:05,920
They used strange weapons like silver hooks.

275
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:08,720
But yesterday, those people used

276
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:10,480
swords.

277
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:14,600
Do you mean they are from Wuji Manor?

278
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:15,680
Impossible.

279
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:25,520
You eavesdrop even at your home.

280
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:27,960
Qin Sang.

281
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,520
You persuaded Ziyan to stay.

282
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:34,960
You took Lu Ping and made him missing.

283
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:36,840
Now you suspect my father.

284
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:39,980
Do you cooperate with people in this way?

285
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,440
What are you doing?

286
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,840
We don’t fight with our companions.

287
00:19:43,840 --> 00:19:45,440
We only prove it by evidence.

288
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:47,880
Don’t you want to end it fast

289
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:49,200
and be with Ziyan?

290
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:52,640
We have come to the manor for two days

