00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:39,820
He’s also a poor guy imprisoned here.

587
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:42,580
Unfortunately, he is insane.

588
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:43,960
He remembered nothing

589
00:40:43,960 --> 00:40:45,640
in the past more than ten years.

590
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,170
Old White forged iron here.

591
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:49,660
He changed the direction of the water

592
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:51,140
so that I could come in.

593
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,520
Don’t bother.

594
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:57,940
We can’t go out.

595
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,210
I don’t believe.

596
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:04,960
The sword…

597
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:07,000
is a waste.

598
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:09,800
Mine is good.

599
00:41:11,240 --> 00:41:12,480
Yes, yours is good.

600
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:34,400
He can make swords

601
00:41:35,120 --> 00:41:36,380
and calls you brother.

602
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:39,200
He has been here for more than ten years.

603
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:40,440
Isn’t he…

604
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,730
Lu Ping, what’s wrong with you?

605
00:41:46,440 --> 00:41:48,480
Mo Lin left me some drugs

606
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:51,560
which will be rejected by my body

607
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:54,560
if I am poisoned.

608
00:41:59,400 --> 00:42:00,060
It’s dirty.

609
00:42:05,960 --> 00:42:06,680
Snowy weed.

610
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:08,640
Do you know it?

611
00:42:09,680 --> 00:42:10,280
That’s OK.

612
00:42:10,440 --> 00:42:11,140
It just causes stomachache.

613
00:42:11,140 --> 00:42:12,600
You will be OK in a few days.

614
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:17,360
It is not fatal.

615
00:42:17,600 --> 00:42:20,560
If we want to stop those

616
00:42:22,120 --> 00:42:24,240
who know the secret from telling it out,

617
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:25,640
we will give them the weed

618
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:28,520
in case it is not appropriate to kill them.

619
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:31,280
They will lose their mind if taking it for long.

620
00:42:31,440 --> 00:42:33,040
They will forget their past.

621
00:42:33,160 --> 00:42:35,200
Even forget who they are.

622
00:42:36,160 --> 00:42:37,960
I have eaten

623
00:42:39,720 --> 00:42:41,000
the food served

624
00:42:41,560 --> 00:42:43,490
to Old White since I have been here.

625
00:42:58,160 --> 00:42:59,680
If I am right,

626
00:43:00,320 --> 00:43:01,000
he is

627
00:43:01,680 --> 00:43:03,240
Lyu Chenfeng.

628
00:43:09,920 --> 00:43:10,520
What?

629
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:13,820
He is Lyu Chenfeng, Master of Tianquan Peak.

630
00:43:14,120 --> 00:43:15,520
He is the reason

631
00:43:15,520 --> 00:43:16,360
why I came to Wuji Manor.

